" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>Frontend &amp; Backend Development</li></ul></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><a href=\"/#contact\"><button class=\"w-full bg-primary  text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300\">Get Consultation<!-- --> </button></a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between border-b-4 border-light\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center mb-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 bg-primary p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg\"><svg class=\"h-8 w-8 text-white\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M9 3v.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 5 0v-.5h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2zm2 2h2v10h-2V5z\"></path></svg></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-zinc -700 ml-4\">Business AI Automation</h2></div><p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Leverage the power of Artificial Intelligence to automate repetitive tasks, optimize workflows, and gain deeper insights, driving efficiency and innovation within your business.</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-600\"><li class=\"flex items-center\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>Workflow Automation</li><li class=\"flex items-center\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>AI-Powered Analytics</li><li class=\"flex items-center\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>Customer Service Chatbots</li><li class=\"flex items-center\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>Predictive Modeling</li><li class=\"flex items-center\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mr-2\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg>Intelligent Data Processing</li></ul></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><a href=\"/#contact\"><button class=\"w-full bg-primary  text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300\">Get Consultation<!-- --> </button></a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between border-b-4 border-light\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center mb-4\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0 bg-primary p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg\"><svg class=\"h-8 w-8 text-white\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-6h2v6zm0-8h-2V7h2v2z\"></path></svg></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-zinc -700 ml-4\">Website Optimization</h2></div><p class